Supported symbologies:

* Code 25
  * Interleaved
  * IATA
* Code 39
* Code 93
* Code 128
  * GS1 128
* EAN-13
  * Bookland
  * UPC-A
* EAN-8
* UPC/EAN supplemental, 2 & 5 digits

* QR Code
* DataMatrix (Semacode)
* PDF417 (requires JRuby)
